cs.PL, cs.SE, cs.AR, cs.LG, cs.DC

The paper focuses on program synthesis and constraint generation for library portability, which falls under the category of programming languages (cs.PL) and software engineering (cs.SE). The paper also discusses the use of these techniques in scientific computing (cs.AR) and deep learning (cs.LG), which are both relevant sub-categories. Finally, the paper deals with the challenges of heterogeneous computing, which could be classified under distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC).
